reviewText: i love theses movies i grew up with them.
Best fight movie ever seen! besides the whole stupid backyard wrestling part in the movie... It is for real fights that just happen to be caught on tape.

There was a good mix of fights on here. Some of them were hilarious like the 300 pound woman showing great boxing skills as she destroys a crackhead. Another funny one was these two rednecks going at it, fighitng dirty, throwing rocks, and being idiots. A good video to put in during a pre-party with your boys.
